<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ài de lèi shuǐ, jī dòng de lèi shuǐ, liú chū wú shù shǒu ài de shī.
 yī shuāng shuāng yǎn jīng, shǎn shuò zhe guāng máng. yī kē kē xīn, tiào dòng zài yī qǐ.
 wǒ men gòng tóng jǔ qǐ, fú yīn de dà qí tà biàn hé shān yáng zhēn lǐ.
 wǒ men tóng zǒu wǒ men tóng qù, zài zhǔ róng yào de dà guāng lǐ.</lyrics>
<title>jǔ qǐ fú yīn de dà qí 迦南50</title>
<hymn_number>50</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>